{"tid":1784982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【VAR之過】高普︰球隊入波時我唔再慶祝！","createTime":"2019-12-16T05:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T07:00:34.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"43aa4ef561487b1d1308c5a98537f0d5299ee1d6","tid":1784982,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:15:24.000Z","msg":"利物浦周六憑穆罕默德沙拿梅開二度，於主場以2:0輕取屈福特，今季在英超保持不敗。不過，在沙拿於90分鐘射入第二球前，沙迪奧文尼於下半場初段曾經破網，惟經VAR判定越位在先，入球無效。<br />\n<br />\n被問到VAR有關的裁決，高普表示︰「我仍未看，你可以想像當以2:0取勝，我對此是不太在意。」他稱︰「老實說，我對它哪裏越位毫無頭緒。我不再在球隊入球後慶祝，因為你必須等到有人說這是一個入球。」「我以為之前有一次傳球可能越位了，但我看不到沙迪奧越位。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/1fef2da92ad975149b5751d6848b1ec9/tenor.gif?itemid=12323227\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F1fef2da92ad975149b5751d6848b1ec9%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D12323227&h=ad0bcd43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be9299f8c1a20a5b9af36b200039e90612eb881b","tid":1784982,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa923c186ede6c46f89b5eb6224b7047ccabd20","tid":1784982,"uid":124277,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"越來越串, 唔講以為拎左冠軍"},{"pid":"e12be653639cb4a735939a33b88f0738f3afc235","tid":1784982,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8fa923c186ede6c46f89b5eb6224b7047ccabd20","tid":1784982,"uid":124277,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"越來越串, 唔講以為拎左冠軍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fb38cf30bdddaf6be28e15fb7cfb1216e78951","tid":1784982,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fa923c186ede6c46f89b5eb6224b7047ccabd20","tid":1784982,"uid":124277,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T